memberdef.name: SIMPLE_ASSERT
memberdef.initializer: do { \ const bool result = EXP; \ if( ! result ) { \ std::cerr << "Expression \"" << #EXP \ << "\" failed the evaluation" << std::endl; \ return 1; \ } \ } while( 0 )

briefdescription.para: Helper macro for evaluating logical tests.
Helper operator that is apparently missing from the base code.
